{"tid":2379943,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】攬炒巴=連登曹操 新作《倫敦行》","createTime":"2021-01-25T14:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T15:24:49.000Z","uid":11294,"like":18,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a3de8644da9f93a5bdb3a7025698d036646e5755","tid":2379943,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:05:32.000Z","msg":"攬鈔當歌，人生幾何？<br />\n兒登水魚，冇人嫌多。<br />\n買完跑車，戶口歸零。<br />\n何以解貧？唯有掠水。<br />\n綠綠銀子，悠悠我心。<br />\n政策倡議，鳩噏至今。<br />\n時事玩具，炒撚晒車。<br />\n我有死忠，含吹奶啜。<br />\n億億港紙，何時奪完？<br />\n錢從豬來，可一可再。<br />\n橫跨歐陸，酒店豪嘆。<br />\n狼吞虎嚥，心念丹麥。<br />\n醉漢扑頭，將計就計。<br />\n腎上腺素，毫無破綻？<br />\n錢不厭多，橋不厭舊。<br />\n劉公吹雞，天下課金。"},{"pid":"a4360db8612c9d01007cf9ecd6c3b624470339c3","tid":2379943,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bbeb24255acd6a751d535cea21aee1e96d5771c","tid":2379943,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b074b5b8c141a8bb09163c8acfb4b2749659324a","tid":2379943,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e850c5fb45fc906c75da12fcaa59eaf52b62edc1","tid":2379943,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b074b5b8c141a8bb09163c8acfb4b2749659324a","tid":2379943,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:09:31.